short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Free Website SEO Checker. On click 'Free SEO audit' button, a new tab opens in seltech.io and the site is checked for SEO results.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension helps users easily and quickly check SEO performance of a site. After installing the extension, clicking the "Free SEO audit" button opens a new tab in the browser and makes a request to a server from which information about the site from which the button was clicked is obtained.
